snippet.title: RCB Goes GREEN! | #IPL2024 Trades & Retentions | Cricket Chaupaal
snippet.description:
It was a lot of drama on the Deadline Day as the #IPL2024 Retentions and Releases were announced. Some surprise retentions and some big names released ahead of the Auctions on Dec 19th. With the Trade deadline set at 12th December, Hardik Pandya finally completed his move back to Mumbai Indians, with RCB buying Cameron Green. All of that, and India's convincing win over Australia in the 2nd T20I, in today's Cricket Chaupaal. 



Watch today's episode of #AakashVani right here:
https://www.jiocinema.com/see-all/aakashvani/13003

Join me on Telegram here: https://t.me/AakashChopraOfficial

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 02 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - 25th November 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 02 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 25th November 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

snippet.title: The Bhopal Gas Leak | Who were Railway Men? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Unveil the chilling account of the Bhopal gas tragedy that shook the world on December 3, 1984. This eye-opening video exposes the horrifying aftermath of the poisonous gas leak from the Union Carbide plant, engulfing over 40 square kilometers and affecting a staggering 200,000 lives. Delve into the chaos and heart-wrenching stories from Bhopal Junction railway station, where Deputy Station Superintendent Ghulam Dastagir's heroic efforts amidst the confusion stood as a beacon of hope. Witness the harrowing long-term impact on countless lives, including Dastagir's tragic demise in 2003 due to health complications. Embark on this chilling journey with Dhruv Rathee as he unravels the haunting narrative of the Bhopal gas tragedy.

Link to the mentioned video :
Bhopal Gas Tragedy | Who was Responsible? | Dhruv Rathee -  https://youtu.be/mcdIV1eWjJg?si=JZ_RygVMBa4e_gmM

The Mahaparv of Bihar is here and I wanted to witness it since a very long time. So this time I just booked my tickets in advance and reached the infamous gun capital of Bihar, Munger. To experience Chhatt Puja like a local with native people of the land

Chhatti Maiyaa ki jai üôèüèº
==========================================================

Heading onto a new journey, that's shape me inside out :) 

What is Melodies of India? 

Magic Monkey, a new age travel YouTube channel travelled and explored by Raunaq Sahni is thrilled to announce an extraordinary and ambitious project. In the quest to unravel the soul of India, Raunaq embarks on a six-month odyssey across the country, meticulously documenting the essence of what it truly means to be Indian. 

The "Melodies of India" project as envisioned by Raunaq is an expedition that aims to capture the heart and spirit of India, transcending its deep-rooted cultures into a visually captivating series of photographs and videos, each narrating a unique facet of our incredible nation. These photographs and videos will serve as visual testimonies, encapsulating the diversity, traditions, and modernisation of India. 

He will later publish 11 photographs along with the moving stories in a Photobook.

So if you want to learn to think like an engineer and have a really fun time doing it, check out the current promotion where you get 2 FREE boxes at https://crunchlabs.com/octopus

snippet.title: Shayarana | Kayden Sharma | MTV Hustle 03 REPRESENT
snippet.description:
"Shayarana" by Kayden Sharma seamlessly merges Shayari (poetry) with Hip-Hop, creating a captivating and melodious track with love as its central theme. 

Credits 
Track Name: Shayarana
Written & Performed By: @kaydensharma 
Music Producer: @anuragsaikia6277 
Co-Composer: Kayden Sharma, Oblong Sioni, Ankur Jyoti

Music Label: @tseries 

Genre: Hip Hop

Sub-Genre: Rap

Language: Hindi

Country Of Origin/Source: India

Mix and Mastered by: Hanish Taneja (Studio Alika)

üëâ Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mtvhustle/ 

#MTVHustle03 #MTVHustle #Kayden 

Lyrics

ANDAZ TERA KHOOBSURAT BESABAR YE ROOH MERI
TADAPTA RAATON MEIN TAB TU EK LAUTI SUKOON MERI
KAL KU BADA MAHAL BANAKE KHUD ICH USME KHO GAYA TOH
TU ICH HAI WOH JO UDHAR BHI MEKU DHOOND LETI

IMAARAT YEH LADKA TERA PYAAR USKI EENTE
NEEND MEIN BHI MEKU TERI KHUSHBOO ROZ KHEENCHE
YEH SHAYAR KI SHAYARI KE ALAG HAI TAREEKE 
RHYME AATI NAHI NAZAR MEIN PHIR BHI FANAA HOTI INPE

KARUN TERI TAREEFAAN TOH KABHI KHATAM NAHI HOTI
TERE PE LIKHNE AAYA TOH PHIR GHAZAL BHI PAD JAATI CHHOTI
MERI YE RAGON MEIN TU DAUD TI NASHA BANKE
JAB MAIN HOTA CHOKE TU AAJATI HAWA BANKE

BANKE REHNA CHAHTA MAIN TERI SAREE KA FALL
RAPPER HOON ISLIYE BOHOT BOLTU LEKIN TERE AAGE MOUN
TU NAHI MADHURI NA MAIN SALMAN PHIR KYON AATA YEH SAWAL
KI HUM AAPKE HAIN KOUN

SABH RAKHTI MERE PE DHYAAN PAR TU RAKHTI MERA DHYAAN 
KAISE SAMJHAOUN KI MAIN KITNA PYAAR KARTA TERE SE
ITTEFAQ HAI KI LADKI HAI TU WARNA LADKA BHI HOTI TOH UTTA ICH PYAAR KARTA TERE SE

HOTA NAHI LIMIT MEIN
DUNIYA GHUMNA CHAHTA MAIN EK NAHI DO TICKET PE
DEKH KE TERI SAADGI KALAM NAHI RUKI TOH
TERE CHARITRA KE CHITRA KO MAIN BAYAAN KARRA LIKHIT MEIN

ADA WOH TERI UFF HAAYE RAMA
MERI RANI TU SHEHER KA MAIN BADSHAH                                         
HIP HOP KAROON WOH BHI SHAYARANA
SEEDHE MAUT DAALU MEHFIL MEIN POORE BOLTE WAH WAH

TU KOI AUR NAI TU MAIN KHUD ICH HOON 
AB TU ICH BOL KI MAIN KHUDKU KAISA CHHOD SAKTA
YOU KNOW TEKU DEKH KE KAISA LAGTA MEKU 
J CHHORD SHABDON MEIN NAHI BOL SAKTA

SOLO KARTA THA PAR AB KARNA HAI DUET 
POORI ZINDAGI TERE SATH REH SAKTA BINA TEKU CHHUE
TRUST ME WHEN I SAY KI MERA HEART PURE HAI 
UPAR SE MERI KUNDALI MEIN RAJYOG HAI

TERE CHEHRE PE HAI SAADGI NIGAHON MEIN SHARARATI
ZULFON MEIN ULJHAN AUR PAYAL KARTI CHHAN CHHAN 
KAALI KURTI PE WOH LAAL CHUNI DAALKE JAB CHALTI
TERE KADMO KE SAATH CHALTI DHADKAN

JANNAT SE KAM NAHI JI HASSI TERE CHEHRE PE 
ZINDA HOON ABHI TAK KYONKI ROZ MARTA TERE PE
EHSAAN KARKE GINTI NAHI WILD HAI PAR CHINDI NAHI
THAKURAINE HAI TU AADESH KAR VINTI NAHI

PATNI MERI BANKE JAB AAYENGI TU GHAR PE 
YEH HOTA JABH MAIN WAPAS AATA DUNIYA BADAL KE
DAAYAN HAATH REHTA MERA EK DIN FALAK PE
PAR BAAYAN HAATH REHTA TERE HAATH KO PAKAD KE

ISSHAARE TUMHARE SAMAJH NAHI AA RAHE
BHULARE BHULARE
LINE BHUL GAYA RE
CHHUTA RE CHHUTA RE
LINE CHHUT GAYA RE
PAR TERE NASHE MEIN KHUCHH BHI GUNGUNA RE

ADA WOH TERI UFF HAAYE RAMA
MERI RANI TU SHEHER KA MAIN BADSHAH
HIP HOP MEIN BHI KARUN SHAYARANA
SEEDHE MAUT DAALU MEHFIL MEIN POORE BOLTE WAH WAH

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3937 | 24 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3937: ACP Ki Biwi Ko Di Dhamki
--------------------------------------------------------
Chalu Pandey informs Jetha that a complaint has been filed against him by an Ahmedabad resident. Jagruti is the wife of a well-known cop who has been threatened by Jetha, Bagha, and Nattu Kaka. Chalu Pandey plays voice recordings of Jetha and Bagha speaking badly. Champaklal and the other Gokuldham men are taken aback by Pandey's proof. Jetha, Bagha, and Nattu Kaka acknowledge that the tapes contain their voices, but they had no intention of threatening a woman. So, how are they going to prove their innocence?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3937, 24 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

*****Dr. Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the ‚ÄúBest emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

*****Dr. Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the ‚ÄúBest emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
